description: Add support for ``aws ecs``, the Amazon EC2 Container Service (ECS)
Add Encryption at Rest and CloudHSM Support.
Update ``aws cloudsearch`` command to latest version
Fix issue where wait commands did not stop waiting when a success state was reached. (`botocore issue 426 <https://github.com/boto/botocore/pull/426>`_)
Allow binary files to be passed to ``--user-data`` (`botocore issue 416 <https://github.com/boto/botocore/pull/416>`_)
Add ``--suggest-query`` option to fix the argument being shadowed by the top level ``--query`` option. (`issue 1068 <https://github.com/aws/aws-cli/pull/1068>`__)
Fix issue with endpoints for ``eu-central-1`` and ``cn-north-1`` (`botocore issue 423 <https://github.com/boto/botocore/pull/423>`__)

Fix issue where empty XML nodes are now parsed as an empty string ``""`` instead of ``null``, which allows for round tripping ``aws s3 get/put-bucket-lifecycle`` (`issue 1076 <https://github.com/aws/aws-cli/issues/1076>`__)
